# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AnimeAgent — Git ignore rules
# 说明：以下文件/目录属于本地环境、敏感信息、构建产物或运行时数据，
#       不应提交到 GitHub。需要保留模板的已使用 *.example 形式。
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Secrets & local environment
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/

# IDE / Editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

# Claude / local agent settings
.claude/

# Database & runtime data
*.db
*.db-journal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Logs
logs/
*.log

# Coverage & test artifacts
.coverage
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.dmypy.json
dmypy.json
.pre-commit-cache/

# Frontend
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
frontend/dist-ssr/
frontend/logs/
*.local

# Debug / ad-hoc payload files (运行/测试时生成的临时 JSON/TXT)
*_payload*.json
ep_status*.json
ep_status*.txt
episode_status.json
human_input.*
nyaa_entries.json
rss_*.txt
torrent_title.txt

# Build / lock artifacts (保留 uv.lock 作为依赖锁定，忽略其他)
# uv.lock 已纳入版本控制，请勿忽略
